  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2018-1421<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2018-11-21</p><hr><p>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nHer Excellency the Governor General in Council, on&nbsp;the&nbsp;recommendation of the Prime Minister, pursuant to paragraph 2(a) of the <em>Public Service Rearrangement and Transfer of Duties Act</em>, transfers&nbsp;from the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development, to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Minister of State to assist the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern&nbsp;Development, the powers, duties and functions of the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development under the following Acts:  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(a) the <em>Arctic Waters Pollution Prevention Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(b) the <em>Canada Lands Surveys Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(c) the <em>Canada Oil and Gas Operations Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(d) the <em>Territorial Lands Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(e) the <em>Dominion Water Power Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(f) the <em>Canada Petroleum Resources Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(g) the <em>Gwich’in Land Claim Settlement Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(h) the <em>Nunavut Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(i) the <em>Nunavut Land Claims Agreement Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(j) the <em>Sahtu Dene and Metis Land Claim Settlement Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(k) the <em>Yukon First Nations Land Claims Settlement Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(l) the <em>Yukon Surface Rights Board Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:right;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n…/2\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n- 2 -\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(m) the <em>Mackenzie Valley Resource Management Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(n) the <em>Yukon Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(o) the <em>Nunavut Waters and Nunavut Surface Rights Tribunal Act</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(p) the <em>Tlicho Land Claims and Self-Government Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(q) the <em>Nunavut Planning and Project Assessment Act</em>;  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n(r) the <em>Northwest Territories Act</em>.  \n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSur recommandation du premier ministre et en vertu de l’alinéa 2a) de la <em>Loi sur les restructurations et les transferts d’attributions dans l’administration publique</em>, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil&nbsp;transfère du ministre des Affaires indiennes et du&nbsp;Nord&nbsp;canadien au ministre d’État délégué auprès du ministre des&nbsp;Affaires indiennes et du Nord canadien, les attributions prévues aux&nbsp;lois suivantes&nbsp;:\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\na) la <em>Loi sur la prévention de la pollution des eaux arctiques</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nb) la <em>Loi sur l’arpentage des terres du Canada</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nc) la <em>Loi sur les opérations pétrolières au Canada</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nd) la <em>Loi sur les terres territoriales</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\ne) la <em>Loi sur les forces hydrauliques du Canada</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nf) la <em>Loi fédérale sur les hydrocarbures</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\ng) la <em>Loi sur le règlement de la revendication territoriale des&nbsp;Gwich’in</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nh) la <em>Loi sur le Nunavut</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\ni) la <em>Loi concernant l’Accord sur les revendications territoriales du&nbsp;Nunavut</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nj) la <em>Loi sur le règlement de la revendication territoriale des Dénés et Métis du Sahtu</em>;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:right;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n…/2\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n- 2 -\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nk) la <em>Loi sur le règlement des revendications territoriales des&nbsp;premières nations du Yukon</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nl) la <em>Loi sur l’Office des droits de surface du Yukon</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nm) la <em>Loi sur la gestion des ressources de la vallée du Mackenzie</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nn) la <em>Loi sur le Yukon</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\no) la <em>Loi sur les eaux du Nunavut et le Tribunal des droits de&nbsp;surface du Nunavut</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\np) la <em>Loi sur les revendications territoriales et l’autonomie gouvernementale du peuple tlicho</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nq) la <em>Loi sur l’aménagement du territoire et l’évaluation des projets au Nunavut</em>;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"margin-left:0.50in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nr) la <em>Loi sur les Territoires du Nord-Ouest</em>.</p>\n\n<p></p><form method=\"post\" action=\"index.php\"><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Back to Form\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" name=\"return\"></form>\t\t\n        <!-- end main content -->\n        <div id=\"def-preFooter\">\n       \t\t<!-- Write closure fall-back static file -->\n             <!--Response.Write readFile(\"StaticFallbackFiles/gcweb/preFooter-\" & $lang & \".html\") -->\n        </div>\n\t\t<!-- Write closure template -->\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n            var defPreFooter = document.getElementById(\"def-preFooter\");\n            defPreFooter.outerHTML = wet.builder.preFooter({\n                cdnEnv: \"prod\",\n                dateModified: \"2022-07-11\",\n                showPostContent: true\n            });\n        </script>\n    "
